# Bitstream app (`extension/src/webview/bitstream-app`)

## Dual-runtime parity (Bitstream / Simulator, dev / VSIX)

**Mandatory:** **`.cursor/rules/bitstream-dual-runtime.mdc`**.

- **Route lifecycle:** `bridge/telemetryModeLifecycle.ts`, `bitstream2/telemetry/route`
- **Ingest:** `shouldIngestTelemetryForRoute()` + `shouldAcceptBs2SampleOrigin()` in `utils/bitstreamTelemetryTransport.ts`
- **BS2 cfg (v0.1):** webview **`SENSOR_CFG_SET`** apply is **local draft** only; wire restore is backlog
- **Simulator:** external **bitstream-simulator** VSIX — not in-bridge mock

## Documentation

- **English only** for `docs/**` under this tree
- Telemetry / transport: **`extension/docs/TELEMETRY_MODE_LIFECYCLE.md`**

## Shared TypeScript types

- App-wide contracts → **`bitstream-app/types/`**
- Per-sensor only → **`components/<sensor>/types.ts`**

## Naming

Do **not** use **“chrome”** for card UI — use **frame** / **shell** / **card frame**.

## Preview model URLs

**`components/3d-rotation/shared/resolveWebviewModelAssetUrl.ts`** — canonical for Bitstream + Sensor Studio GLB paths. See **`extension/docs/ASSETS_LOCATION_SYSTEM.md`**.

## Communication

**Always DO NOT respond in Chinese.** Use **English** and/or **Thai** only — **`communication-language.mdc`**.
